Properties.Description:
Commander, you may want to consider retiring some of your heroes, personnel, and schematics to make room for new recruits and weapon innovations.

Slotting people and schematics will permanently remove them from action. However, once you complete a collection category, you will receive new rewards!

To place an item in your Collections:
Select Armory
Select Collection Book
Navigate to the appropriate collection slot
Select the item to place in the slot
